  "detailed_description": "<strong>The Dungeon Power is a <span class=\"bb_strike\">VERY EXTREME</span> challenging 3D-Isometric Platformer</strong> where you must to get through deadly rooms in order to advance and escape from a gigantic cursed dungeon.<br><br><i>Timing your actions, taking chances and tilting hard is required to overcome this trial and face the<strong> Dungeon Master</strong>!</i><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/3f11f9d6729a81158ce49de2ff0595a6.poster.avif?t=1501979334\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/3f11f9d6729a81158ce49de2ff0595a6.webm?t=1501979334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/3f11f9d6729a81158ce49de2ff0595a6.mp4?t=1501979334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features</strong></h2></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Over 30 Levels of Challenge<br></li><li> Normal Pacing Mode, for a classic experience.<br></li><li> Fast Paced Mode, 2x Speed for a faster gameplay.<br></li><li> Powerful Bosses! You're nearly defenseless against them!<br></li><li> Sensitive Control, Sensitive Jump, Air Control and Movement, everything matters!<br></li><li> Straight to the Point! No Dialogues, no Interruptions.<br></li><li> Time Attack! (Gold, Silver and Bronze time for a higher achievement)</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Take this Challenge!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/21455599e00eed1e302322b7e490b029.poster.avif?t=1501979334\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/21455599e00eed1e302322b7e490b029.webm?t=1501979334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/21455599e00eed1e302322b7e490b029.mp4?t=1501979334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/46a80c864df745bf07e1c6a4318c7610.poster.avif?t=1501979334\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/46a80c864df745bf07e1c6a4318c7610.webm?t=1501979334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/46a80c864df745bf07e1c6a4318c7610.mp4?t=1501979334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/ed77a38b318de6abc8351fc636fec670.poster.avif?t=1501979334\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/ed77a38b318de6abc8351fc636fec670.webm?t=1501979334\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/669960/extras/ed77a38b318de6abc8351fc636fec670.mp4?t=1501979334\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
